'''Measure 4213.0410''' was a proposal brought to the senate by [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Jorus C'baoth]], and passed by [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] in [[28 BBY/Legends|8:2:11]]. The Measure was used in order to sponsor and launch the [[Outbound Flight Project]], in addition to providing full funding for the project.

